Google Chrome: Google Bookmark Extension 
========================================
Chrome extension for convenient sync bookmarks by using Google Bookmarks. Very simple and easy to use but usefull. 

Thanks for using and be happier ;-)
Any comments and suggestions are welcome!

Source Code: http://github.com/solo123/gbm_plugin

Ref:
1) Javascript OOP: https://developer.mozilla.org/en/Introduction_to_Object-Oriented_JavaScript
2) Chrome extension: http://code.google.com/chrome/extensions/
3) Google bookmarks API: http://lnkr.mobi/bm/google_bookmarks_api/

